                    <l n="d">na hi pu<lb n="59"/><unclear>ruṣai</unclear>ḥ para-kīrttayo villopyāḥ<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></l>
                </lg>
             <p>sraṣṭā yas tu guṇātmakas tad-adhi</p>  
             <lg n="19" met="śārdūlavikrīḍita">
