             </lg>
             <p>   <lb n="63"/>parama-māheśvara-parama-bhaṭṭāraka-mahārāja-parameśva<supplied reason="omitted">ra</supplied>-soma-kula-ti<lb n="64" break="no"/>laka-trikaliṅgādhipati--śrī-<persName><choice><sic>j</sic><corr>y</corr></choice>ayāti</persName>-rājadeva-pravarddhamāna-v<choice><sic>e</sic><corr>i</corr></choice>jaya-rājye<lb n="65"/>navame samvatsare <num value="9">9</num> jyeṣṭha-<choice><orig>ś</orig><reg>s</reg></choice>ita-trayodaśyā<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <num value="13">10 3</num> <supplied reason="omitted">divasa</supplied>ḥ Utkīrṇṇā<lb n="66"/>vijñān<choice><sic>ī</sic><corr>i</corr></choice>-<persName>mādhavene</persName>t<choice><sic>ī</sic><corr>i</corr></choice> Om Om<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
